        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>firecracker cauliflower stir-fry </strong>over the<strong> warmed edamame & jasmine rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>roasted peanuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
